----------------------------------------------
                OPTIMIZATION TECHNICS
-------------------------------------------------------------
                    VACUUM
VACUUM - delta keeps older files[versions] for time travel but old data biulds up -- so we can clean them using - 
                VACUUM table_name RETAIN 24 HOURS; -- defult 7 days
helps to remove unnecessary files -- reduce storage cost

Before VACUUM:
Data v1 → Data v2 → Data v3
(old files still exist)

After VACUUM:
Only latest needed files remain
you cannot time travel to versions whose data files were deleted.

------------------------------------------------------------
                    OPTIMIZE
compacts many small files into big files -- improve read performance
                    Z-ORDER
sort the data based on the column to make searches faster
query - OPTIMIZE table_name ZORDER BY col_name

